snippet.title: My First Game is on Steam! - Button Pop Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out Button Pop on Steam now! :
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2244400/Button_Pop/

Button Pop is a mash up between a Tower defence, Button masher and a idle game where you are the main button and you have to defend yourself again all the other little jealous buttons coming to get you!

Music from :  
TrackTribe - Walk With Me
